said anatoly znamensky a 66yearold retired taxi driver 
vegetables fruit cheese butter meat they appear and 
disappear but with bread there was never a problem until now 
the lack of bread comes on the heels of a summerlong shortage 
of tobacco that has led to street demonstrations in moscow and 
leningrad strikes in other russian cities and a riot in a ural 
mountains city 
