off with hubble the other time was just before the challenger 
accident 
nasa must launch discovery between oct 5 and oct 23 to take 
advantage of earths alignment with the sun and jupiter otherwise 
the mission will have to wait 13 months ulysses is being sent on a 
fiveyear journey to explore the suns poles 
