pittsburgh press attorney scott e henderson said 
this will make it easier for the public and press to view 
those parts of the judicial process he said 
the superior court decision said the newspaper does not have 
access to discovery documents or information developed by the 
two sides in a case to prepare for trial 
the case is based on a lawsuit filed by an akron ohio man who 
