colonynewport national bank in 1986 
under the agreement citizens will acquire 600 million of 
selected old colony assets while bank of new england keeps 550 
million in assets it will also acquire more than 900 million in 
deposits while bank of new england keeps about 250 million in 
deposits liabilities and capital 
